public LbsProperties(@Named(value="LBS.apiKey") @Nonnull

                             @Named(value="LBS.geoCodeUrl1") @Nonnull
                             String geoCodeUrl1,
                             @Named(value="LBS.geoCodeUrl2") @Nonnull
                             String geoCodeUrl2,
                             @Named(value="LBS.tileMapUrl") @Nonnull
                             String tileMapUrl,
                             @Named(value="LBS.routeUrl1") @Nonnull
                             String routeUrl1,
                             @Named(value="LBS.trafficEnabled")
                             boolean trafficEnabled,
                             @Named(value="LBS.numberOfRouteActors")
                             int numberOfRouteActors)
                      throws InvalidPropertyValueException
        LBS properties.
        Parameters:
        apiKey - API key to use for LBS connector. Cannot be empty.
        geoCodeUrl1 - URL of geocoding service version 1. Must include "http://" and be a valid URL.
        geoCodeUrl2 - URL of geocoding service version 2. Must include "http://" and be a valid URL.
        tileMapUrl - URL of tile mapping service. Must include "http://" and be a valid URL.
        routeUrl1 - URL of routing service version 1. Must include "http://" and be a valid URL.
        trafficEnabled - if true, consider traffic jams in routing calls.
        numberOfRouteActors - Number of route actors to use, for parallel requests to LBS. Must be > 0.
        Throws:
        InvalidPropertyValueException
